title: A Review of Episode 1209 Anthony Cumia
description:
Anthony from the legendary Opie and Anthony radio show. Was the main inspiration for Joe to start his podcast.  Joe talks about how he was inspired to create his own podcast which is now one of the biggest in the world. This was a conversation I’ve wanted to review for years.
